  "body": "AsmCodeGen.cpp uses evmasm::Assembly, even though it is in the yul namespace. The evmasm::Assembly is immediately converted to a subclass of AbstractAssembly via the EthAssemblyAdapter. I think the EthAssemblyAdapter should be moved to e.g. the evmasm namespace (inside libevmasm) and then used from the site that calls AsmCodeGen, so that AsmCodeGen just receives an AbstractAssembly instance.",
